## Summary
Ability to hide HomeIndicator from iPhone X, XR, XS on given page

## API Changes
add to Xamarin.Forms.Platform.iOS/PlatformRenderer.cs 
```
public override UIViewController ChildViewControllerForHomeIndicatorAutoHidden
{
	get
	{
	     return (UIViewController)Platform.GetRenderer(this.Platform.Page);
	}
}
... 
public override void ViewDidLoad()
{
       ...
       SetNeedsUpdateOfHomeIndicatorAutoHidden();
}

```
and add new bindable property to page and consume it in Page Renderer

```
[assembly: ExportRenderer(typeof(MyPage), typeof(HomeIndicatorRenderer))]
namespace MyApp
{ 
    public class HomeIndicatorRenderer : PageRenderer
    {
        // new property
        public override bool PrefersHomeIndicatorAutoHidden => this.Element.HomeIndicatorAutoHiddenIOS;

        public override void ViewDidAppear(bool animated)
        {
            base.ViewDidAppear(animated);
            SetNeedsUpdateOfHomeIndicatorAutoHidden();
        }
    }
}
``` 

## Intended Use Case

Applicable to all pages where user don't want to be distracted by home indicator, e.g. full-screen gallery window or full-screen player window.

### Steps to Reproduce

1. Open & run tests/xharness/xharness.sln
2. Run the fsharp/iOS Unified Today Extension 64-bits - device/Debug test
3. Build fails with `bin/iPhone/Debug64-today/TodayContainer.app/PlugIns/fsharp.dll: code object is not signed at all`

### Expected Behavior

Build succeeds

### Actual Behavior

Build [fails](https://gist.github.com/rolfbjarne/80b23dbfedde77edf769e8cd66f7933e):

    /work/maccore/master/xamarin-macios/_ios-build/Library/Frameworks/Mono.framework/External/xbuild/Xamarin/iOS/Xamarin.iOS.Common.targets: error : Tool exited with code: 1. Output: bin/iPhone/Debug64-today/TodayContainer.app/PlugIns/fsharp.dll: code object is not signed at all

There seems to be something overwriting the BuildDependsOn property.

This is from the [F# extension build](https://gist.github.com/rolfbjarne/80b23dbfedde77edf769e8cd66f7933e):

    Project "/work/maccore/master/xamarin-macios/tests/xharness/tmp-test-dir/fsharp-today-extension/fsharp-today-extension.fsproj" (default target(s)):
    		Initial Properties:
    		[...]
    		BuildDependsOn = 
    					BuildOnlySettings;
    					BeforeBuild;
    					CoreBuild;
    					AfterBuild
    

And this is from a working [C# extension build](https://gist.github.com/rolfbjarne/9daead0c98fc9a58357a32760b0deb56):

    Project "/work/maccore/master/xamarin-macios/tests/xharness/tmp-test-dir/link sdk-today-extension/link sdk-today-extension.csproj" (default target(s)):
    		Initial Properties:
    		[...]
    		BuildDependsOn = 
    					BuildOnlySettings;
    					PrepareForBuild;
    					_CollectBundleResources;
    					_OptimizePngImages;
    					_OptimizePropertyLists;
    					_OptimizeLocalizationFiles;
    					_PackLibraryResources;
